race.comment: Race gets taken to pieces by the scratchings with several key winning hopes coming ou in the morning. Leaves the door wide open for BOKEEM (2) who found one better this grade at Terang finishing well and looking right back in form. Quick turnaround into this and gets the right race to convert that nice form into winning form. STIRRUP (5) will be around the mark if he puts his best foot forward and can same the same about BOUDICA WARRIOR (4). LEICA ROCK (11) continues to race well. Just a length away at Colac and this is going to be no tougher. Easier in fact.
